**Docs:** This bead IS the docs deliverable. User-facing guide docs/gates.md plus index/cross-link wiring. No generated docs/cli/* change (no CLI surface change). No planning-doc churn — the schema and runbook are referenced, not edited (behavior is already shipped; nothing to move).

